'''Dyana Gaye''' (wavutse 1975) ni umuyobozi w'amafirime mu [[bufaransa]] ariko aturuka muri [[senegali]].

== Ubuzima bwa Biografiya ==
Gaye yavukiye i Paris mu 1975, umukobwa w’abimukira bo muri Senegali, yiga muri kaminuza ya Paris 8 Vincennes-Saint-Denis yiga filime. <ref>http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/2016/</ref> Yakiriye inkunga ya Louis Lumière - Villa Médicis inkunga mu 1999 kubera amashusho ye ''Une femme pour Souleymane'' . <ref name="africanfilm">https://africanfilmny.org/directors/dyana-gaye/</ref> Gaye yayoboye mu 2000, kandi yahawe igihembo kinini cya Jury mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Dakar. <ref name="gan">http://www.fondation-gan.com/laureats-et-films/gan-laureats/des-etoiles</ref> Mu 2004, yari umwe mu bahatanira umwanya wa Rolex Mentor na Protégé Arts Initiative. Gaye yayoboye filime ngufi ''J'ai deux amours'', mu rwego ''rw'umushinga wa Paris la métisse'' mu 2005. Umwaka ukurikira, yayoboye ''Ousmane'', byagenze neza cyane. Yakiriye nomination ya Filime ngufi nziza muri César Awards. Muri 2009, Gaye yakoze kandi ayobora ''Saint Louis Blues'', yari comedi yumuziki. Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Lokarno na Sundance Film Festival, yari umwe mu batanu ba nyuma ba Filime ngufi nziza muri César Awards. <ref name="africanfilm" /> Filime yatoranijwe, iterwa inkunga kandi ikorwa mubice bigize gahunda yibanze ya Afrika. <ref>https://shadowandact.com/focus-features-africa-first-alumni-dyana-gaye-will-make-her-feature-film-debut-with-des-etoiles-stars/</ref>

Yabaye igihembo cya 2012 cyigihembo cya Gan Foundation. <ref name="gan" /> Gaye yayoboye ''Munsi ya Starry Sky'' muri 2013, abaye film ya mbere yerekana amashusho hagati ya Dakar, Turin, na New York City . Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto maze ahabwa igihembo kinini cya Jury hamwe nigihembo cyabateze amatwi muri Premiers Plans Angers Festival.  Gaye yavuze ko iyi filime ari ugukomeza gukina filime ngufi zabanjirije iyi, no gukora ubushakashatsi ku ndangamuntu nyinshi ndetse n’abinjira. <ref>https://www.wsws.org/en/articles/2013/10/02/tint-o02.html</ref>

Gaye ni umunyamuryango wa Collectif 50/50, umuryango ufite intego yo kugira uburinganire hagati y’abagabo n’abagore mu nganda za firime, ndetse no guteza imbere ubudasa muri sinema. 

